<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="panic-n">panic <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pænɪk/    美 /'pænɪk/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>恐慌；惊慌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The news has caused panic. 
这条消息已引起了恐慌。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hundreds of people left their homes <strong>in (a) panic</strong>.
上百人惊慌地离开了他们的家园。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 5改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>“Tommy, run! Be quick! The house is on fire!” the mother shouted, with <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (恐慌) clearly in her voice.  （2011 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. panic  </p></div>